What you need to know:

Mansur Mohamed Surur alias Mansour is being sought for extradition to answer to five charges related to the offence.Chief Magistrate Martha Mutuku ordered his detention at Capitol Hill Police Station in Nairobi as she analyses several applications by the Director of Public Prosecution (DPP) and the defence.DPP Haji said Mr Mansur will answer to charges of conspiracy to commit wildlife trafficking, wildlife trafficking, money laundering and conspiracy to distribute and possess a controlled substance in violation of several US laws.